IPv6 isn't supported by <a href='https://www.ovh.co.uk/vps/vps-cloud.xml'>OVH Cloud</a>
Those stupid Privacy Extension addresses <a href='https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7217#section-3'>keep changing</a>
I can just <a href='http://ipv4marketgroup.com/ipv4-pricing-in-a-post-arin-runout-world/'>buy</a> more IPv4 addresses
